text: Jönköpings Södra IF is an association football club in the town of Jönköping in Sweden. The club finished up on the second place at Allsvenskan in 1950. The club once again qualifyed for Allsvenskan again on 17 October 2015. ==References== ==Other websites== * Official website Category:1922 establishments in Sweden Category:Swedish football clubs Category:Sport in Jönköping
